inspiracio.xml
Class Element

java.lang.Object
  inspiracio.xml.Element

public class Element
extends Object

Simple representation of an XML element. Similar to DOM, but without using DOM. If you want to manipulate a whole XML-document with DOM; use DOM or JDOM. If you want to make little bits of XML and use toString for formatting, use this.
